1. Welcome to rentooz !
2.1 Rentooz is community based online rental service.
2.2 Earn money by posting products and rent also!
3. Post product which you don't use too frequently on your joined communities.
4. Your product will be available in your joined community but only visible to users who are part of the same community.
5. Person who need the product will send request for renting by specifying number of days and the date.
6. Renting is community based so the you can post a specific product in a specific community only
7. You can approve/reject the request sent by the borrower.
8. If you accept the request, you'll get contact information of the borrower.
9. If you accept the request, you'll get contact information of the borrower and the borrower will get yours.
10. Renting will start on specified date and you don't have to remember anything. The website will manage the whole deal and you'll earn money on day basis.
11. Borrower and giver both will get sharentooz bonus for the deal, you can use these bonus for different offers available in website
12. You'll get notification after deal is over, so the borrower will return the product to you.
13. That's how rentooz works, just the matter of few clicks.